import React from "react"; const Card = ({tempInfo}) => { const { temp, humidity, pressure, weathermoood, name, speed, country, sunset, } = tempInfo; let sec=sunset; let date=new Date(sec*1000); let timeStr = `${date.getHours()}:${date.getMinutes()}`; // console.log(temp); return ( <>
{temp}°
{weathermoood}
{name},{country}
{new Date().toLocaleString()}

{timeStr}
sunset

{humidity}
Humidity

{pressure}
Pressure

{speed}
Speed

); }; export default Card;
